de.must.appletserver
Class SessionData

java.lang.Object
  de.must.appletserver.SessionData
All Implemented Interfaces:
DataObjectConstructionDetails
public class SessionData
extends java.lang.Object
implements DataObjectConstructionDetails

Container to share data between Session and Remotables. Attributes to be shared are declared as public. Thus, they may be accessed as if they were in the respective class. (Since java doesn't provide a read-only pointer to an object, we found get/set formality useless here.) Contains methods to retrieve resources softly: Instead of throwing exceptions runtime errors are logged and the key is given back instead of the found resource. Session comprehensive data should be stored in de.must.middle.GlobalStd.

See Also:
GlobalStd
